snippet.title: The Franz Kafka Videogame Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The puzzle adventure by the award-winning Russian Denis Galanin let's you experience a unique & absurd adventure where nothing is as it seems! Beautiful artwork and mindblowing puzzles await you...

Releasedate: April 6th, 2017

More about the game: http://store.steampowered.com/app/392280/

Official blog: http://kafkagame.blogspot.de/
